    <h2>About the Admin Panel</h2>
    <p>The Admin Panel of Recruitify is a powerful tool designed to give administrators full control over the recruitment process. With a user-friendly interface and a range of powerful features, it allows admins to manage user profiles, job postings, applications, and much more. This central hub enhances efficiency and simplifies the overall management of the recruitment workflow.</p>

    <h3>Features of the Admin Panel</h3>
    <ul>
        <li><strong>User Management:</strong> Admins can easily manage user profiles, including viewing, editing, and updating candidate and employer details.</li>
        <li><strong>Job Postings Management:</strong> Create, edit, and manage job listings across different industries and locations. Admins can control which listings are active and easily update them as needed.</li>
        <li><strong>Application Tracking:</strong> The system tracks applications in real-time, allowing admins to monitor progress, review applicant details, and move candidates through various stages of the recruitment process.</li>
        <li><strong>Interview Scheduling:</strong> Admins can schedule interviews directly through the platform, ensuring seamless communication between candidates and hiring teams.</li>
        <li><strong>Analytics & Reporting:</strong> Access detailed analytics on user activity, job posting performance, and application trends to make data-driven decisions that improve the recruitment process.</li>
        <li><strong>Settings & Customization:</strong> Tailor the platform settings to match the specific needs of your organization, ensuring that all processes align with your business goals.</li>
    </ul>

    <h3>How Admins Can Take Advantage</h3>
    <p>With the Recruitify Admin Panel, administrators gain complete control over the recruitment process. By leveraging the panel's robust features, admins can enhance efficiency, make informed decisions, and streamline every step from job posting to candidate placement. The integration of advanced tools like the application tracking system and interview scheduler enables admins to manage recruitment seamlessly while reducing manual work.</p>
